\begin_inset Formula $s|_{U^{x}}=t|_{U^{x}}$
\end_inset

.
 Clearly, 
\begin_inset Formula $U=\bigcup_{x\in U}U^{x}$
\end_inset

 and therefore 
\begin_inset Formula $s=t$
\end_inset

 by the sheaf axiom.
 
\end_layout

